@marsden_paula Hi Paula,
You can find our live chat and phone number for our support here: https://t.co/b3QIqPBI2R Today you can contact us until 19:00 and we will help you with your case.
Regards Anja

@kaushikghy Hi! 
Unfortunately we can not see or estimate when we will be planning new routes.

Kind regards, Kevin

@MarcopoloLondon Hi!
We recommend you to go by this link for more information about the system,https://t.co/iTM579rP4n or https://t.co/b6TVwwvdS3.

Kind regards, Kevin

@joanna63982307 Hi Joanna!
To purchase an extra seat you need to call in by the phone and they will help you do the booking and buy an extra seat as well, you can find the local number by this link https://t.co/b3QIqPk7bj.

Kind regards, Kevin

@jonlang4 Hej Jonlang4, För att resa inrikes krävs inte något Covid-19 test. Mer information gällande Covid-19 och restriktioner finner du på följande länken,
https://t.co/bG6acgHGid under "If you want to travel" och "Entry Restrictions"

Vänliga hälsningar, Isak

@vaibhavkumar Hi Vaibhavkumar, Please contact us at our customer service on the following link or at Facebook Messenger so we can have a look in to your errand,
https://t.co/b3QIqPk7bj

Kind regards, Isak

@1313consa Hej! Vi kan dessvärre inte vänta in passagerare då det kan orsaka ännu fler förseningar. Om båda flygen är på samma bokning blir du istället ombokad till ett nytt alternativ om du skulle missa din anslutning.

Med vänlig hälsning,
Anton.

@RWC19Celts Hello. I am sorry to hear that your voucher is about to expire. Please contact us via Facebook Messenger or live-chat with your voucher details and we will help you look at what is possible for your voucher.

Best regards,
Anton.

@SamNort42315429 Hello! Please contact us via Facebook Messenger or live-chat with your voucher details and we will help you take a look at what possibilities there are for your voucher.

Best regards,
Anton.

@dsfrederik Hi! 
Yes if you don't get that option on our website then i recommend that you contact our customer service either by phone or by chat so we can help you with that. https://t.co/b3QIqPk7bj

//Best regards, Dennis.

@bjornmellquist Hej!
Nej han kan tyvärr inte resa utan sitt pass. Han behöver ha med sig ett giltigt pass för att kunna resa med oss, man kan resa via Danmark men då behöver man ett negativt Covid-test som är taget inom 24h från första avgång.

//Vänlig hälsning, Dennis.

@MsEvaMarianne Hej! 
Okej ja om du vill så kan du skicka in ett klagomål till vår customer care avdelning på denna länk: https://t.co/VXoFjKd4yl Men annars kan du kontakta oss via chatten om du vill ha mer information om hur du bokar en eurobonus resa.

//Vänlig hälsning, Dennis.

@Francis__Gaby Hi! 
Okay in that case i would recommend that you contact our customer service by chat or phone so we can help you have a look at your options. You can find the contact info here: https://t.co/b3QIqPk7bj

//Best regards, Dennis.

@1313consa Hej! 
Ja det är korrekt, man behöver ha ett negativt test som är taget inom 24h för att resa igenom Danmark just nu.

//Vänlig hälsning, Dennis.

@dhillerstrom Hi! 
Yes that flight has been cancelled. So you can get a full refund or rebook the trip depending on what you want to do. You can cancel and request a refund via our website https://t.co/saQXo2wpQa 

//Best regards, Dennis.

@VickiP45 Hi! 
It's sadly not possible to use the voucher for a hotel instead, i recommend that you contact our customer service via chat or phone so we can have a look at your alternatives. You can see the contact information here: https://t.co/b3QIqPk7bj

//Best regards, Dennis.

@EmmaJan99009292 Hi! 
Okay then i recommend that you contact our customer service by phone so we can help you. You can find the contact information here: https://t.co/b3QIqPk7bj

//Best regards, Dennis.

@LinneaSchossow Hi Linnea! I recommend that you look in to our traffic program to find flights. You can find Direct flights from Dublin to Copenhagen from 2021-05-31.
https://t.co/BmkPFsiEyt

Kind regards, Isak

@DubGot1 Hi Dubgot1, please contact us over Facebook Messenger or our Customer Service that you can find on the following link so we can look in to your errand,
https://t.co/b3QIqPk7bj

Kind regards, Isak

@CBourneJ Hej Clayton
Så fint att höra att det ordnade sig för dig på din resa. Ha en fin dag.

Hälsningar /Anna

@wilshawalex Hi Alex
Contact us by messenger and we can look further at this.

Best regards /Anna

@dearclarissa Hi! 
Yes you can change the booking at latest 72h before the departure without a change fee, this offer doesn't extend to domestic trips, but if you book a trip within Europe or such then there is no problem.

//Best regards, Dennis.

@1313consa Hej!

Ja det stämmer, man har tillgång till Star Alliance lounger vid en europa resa vid köp av en SAS plus biljett, via denna länk kan man hitta vilka lounger som finns ute just nu https://t.co/63gRjhqYUS.

Med vänliga hälsningar, Kevin

@e_extremena Hi!
You will receive a new voucher if the flight get´s cancelled if the last voucher has expired,

Kind regards, Kevin

@KirstineBaloti Hi! 
Here is the local number for Denmark +45 70 102 000.

Kind regards, Kevin

@Alex_skrr Hi!
We recommend you to take contact with us by chat/phone and we will look in to the matter, you can find the local number by this link https://t.co/b3QIqPk7bj.

Kind regards, Kevin

@KirstineBaloti Hi! 
We recommend you to take contact with us over the chat/phone and we will look in to the voucher, you can find the local number by this link https://t.co/b3QIqPk7bj.

Kind regards, Kevin

@huey_bb Hi Huey_bb, Please contact us at Facebook Messenger or at our Customer Service that you can find on the following link so we can look in to your errand.
https://t.co/b3QIqPk7bj

Kind regards, Isak

@Yunning_H Hi Carol
If your ticket is booked with SAS and you cancel it the eligible refund is made to the original payment that was used.

Best regards /Anna

@BuzzTravelBlog Hello Buzzin’ Around the World
How nice to hear about your positive experience. 

Best regards /Anna

@curlykathrine Hi Kathrine
You can find information regarding the limited hand luggage here https://t.co/2UUXPRN2w1
Staff at airport is instructed to check in additional luggage and payment for that can be requested if it is not included in ticket.

@chbyhlin Hej, Möjligheten att boka om en biljett styrs av biljettens regler och om det finns lediga biljetter av samma typ på det plan man vill ändra till. Vår support kan ge svar på varför ombokning inte var möjlig i detta fall https://t.co/z4gOZAAJQJ

Hälsningar,
Peter

@minion_marvel Hi, we do not have any requirements our self for tests. We are unable to provide specific information about entry restrictions imposed by each country. Please contact the local authorities or the country's embassy if you are unsure of the required documents.

Regards
Peter

@Magnus_Persson Hej! Jag beklagar om du upplever att vår kommunikation varit otydlig. Avgiftsfri ombokning gäller på alla internationella resor fram till 72 timmar innan utresa, dock behöver man betala eventuell mellanskillnad om den nya biljetten är dyrare.

Med vänlig hälsning,
Anton.

@Laura60b Hello Laura! Due to current circumstances only one piece of carry on is allowed per person. This means that you can only bring one item in the cabin, both luggage and handbag is not allowed sadly.

Best regards,
Anton.

@becomegreennow Hi Eric 
Contact us on live chat or messenger and we will take a look at this.

Best regards/ Anna

@becomegreennow Hi Eric 
Contact us with your booking information on live chat , messenger or phone https://t.co/b3QIqPk7bj (click on customer service/eurobonus and numbers show) and we will help you further.  

Best regards /Anna

@LaurenGoodban Hi Lauren 
Contact us on live chat, messenger or phone https://t.co/b3QIqPk7bj with your booking reference and we will help you.

Best regards/ Anna

@LiAnnTravels Hi LiAnnTravels
We are happy to help, as you may have noticed you just change market by selecting country at the bottom on the start page if you need another currency.

Best regards/ Anna

@dhillerstrom Hi Daniel
Contact us on liv chat or messenger and we will assist you with this.

Best regards/ Anna

@JoshHH34 Hi Josh
You are welcome to contact us by live chat or messenger and we can take a look at this.

Best regards /Anna

@dipskp Hi Dee
We have big volumes on the phone this weekend. Our customer support is working as hard as they can to answer all calls as soon as possible. If you have not received our help yet you can also contact us via live chat or messenger.

Best regards /Anna

@bellabrannborn Hej

Tack för din synpunkt! Vi ser kontinuerligt över våra tilläggstjänster, inklusive prissättningen, och anpassar dem efter efterfrågan och kundernas behov.

Med vänliga hälsningar,

@Viva10232273 Hello! To send us feedback please use our webform on this link https://t.co/F93CXMjEBn

Best regards,
Anton.

@ShelMillsey I'm sorry about that but we are not able to assist you over Twitter unfortunately. Baggage Service can only be reached by phone.

Best regards,
Anton.

@ShelMillsey I'm sorry if you were encountering communication barriers when calling Baggage Service, they can however unfortunately only be reached by phone.

Best regards,
Anton.

@ShelMillsey Hello, I am sorry to hear that your bags are lost. We are unfortunately not able to assist with this over social media but you can find SAS Baggage Service phone numbers for all airports here https://t.co/ZV9bTNLSZs

Best regards,
Anton.

@AlexSkinner27 Hello. I am terribly sorry to hear that, if you wish to leave feedback to us about your experience I recommend that you use our webform https://t.co/wprQ9YWI1H

Best regards,
Anton.

@MorganMorgans40 Hi! 
I'm sorry to hear that. If you have not received it by now then i recommend that you contact our customer service via chat or by phone. You can find the contact info here: https://t.co/b3QIqPk7bj

//Best regards, Dennis.

@Sun_Devil_87 Hi! 
I am sorry that we couldn't help you fix the flight you wanted. If you want to send us a complaint then i recommend you using this form: https://t.co/VXoFjKd4yl

//Best regards, Dennis.

@AlexSkinner27 Hi!
I'm sorry if the lounge wasn't open, but the best i can recommend is to send in a complaint after your trip. You can use this form: https://t.co/VXoFjKd4yl

//Best regards, Dennis.

@Sun_Devil_87 Hi! 
Okay you can usually rebook the trip without a cost as long as you contact our customer service after a cancellation, but we do have a few rules regarding it. But you can send us a complaint regarding this if you want: https://t.co/VXoFjKd4yl

//Best regards, Dennis.

@Sun_Devil_87 Hi!
I'm sorry if your trip was cancelled and changed. But in that case i recommend that you call our customer service so we can help you have a look at it. You can see our contact info here: https://t.co/b3QIqPk7bj

//Best regards, Dennis.

@ingemoh Hej!
Okej det kan vara så att din email ligger kvar i något gammalt system, så om du ringer oss på 0770 727 727 eller chattar med vår kundtjänst så kan vi kontakta vår eurobonus support och be dom kolla på det åt dig.

//Vänlig hälsning, Dennis.

@ManniGee1971 Hi!
We recommend you to remove the information about you booking reference and take contact with us by phone or chat and we can look in to the matter, you can take contact by this link https://t.co/b3QIqPk7bj

Kind regards, Kevin

@marcnoruega Hej!
Vi på SAS har bara ett krav på ansiktsmask sedan är det upp till det landet, du kan läsa mer om säkerheten via denna länk https://t.co/ftLhtPNT7X och landets krav via denna länk https://t.co/uHgETi2pF7 under "entry restrictions".

Med vänliga hälsningar, Kevin

@LutandoNgqakaza Hi LutandoNgqakaza, Please contact us on our live customer service, you can find contact information on the following link and we will help you further in your errand.
https://t.co/b3QIqPk7bj

Kind regards, Isak

@kentdebruin Hi, f you struggle with navigating our chat, you can contact us over Facebook Messenger or call our support directly
https://t.co/b3QIqPk7bj You find our phone numbers by selecting your region in the drop down menu and click on Customer Service
Kind regards, Rebecka
